                "type": "stat_block_section"
              }
            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The jinx eater gives an eerie croak. Each non-tengu in a 30-foot emanation must succeed at a DC 21 Will save or be clumsy 1 for 1 round (or 1 minute on a critical failure). Regardless of the results, each creature is then temporarily immune to Jinxed Call for 1 minute.",
            "traits": [
